罗汉果，<span class="_ _5"></span>那心识肯定</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y58 ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls1a ws0">要不断延续。<span class="_ _6"></span>所以，<span class="_ _6"></span>心识是独立于身体之外的，<span class="_ _6"></span>这与塔克尔</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 yaf ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">博士所讲的比喻完全一致。 </div><div class="t m0 x1f h4 yb8 ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">此观点有非常严密的逻辑性，<span class="_ _7"></span><span class="ls16">大家应当好好思维。<span class="_ _7"></span><span class="ls0">其实，</span></span></div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y5b ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">“意识是大脑的产物”这种说法，很早以前就站不住脚了，</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y5c ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">倘若它真的合理，<span class="_ _4"></span>那无头众生为什么还能活着？在上个世纪</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y5d ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls17 ws0">40<span class="_ _0"> </span>年代，<span class="_ _7"></span><span class="ls18">美国就有一只被斩掉头的鸡，<span class="_ _1f"></span><span class="ls0">它<span class="_ _3"> </span>18<span class="_ _0"> </span>个月都没有死。</span></span></div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.500000,0.000000,0.000000,1.500000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
